problem_text: Refer to trapezoid C D F G with median H E. Let W X be the median of C D E H. Find W X.
source: Textbook 2_Chapter 11 - Areas of Polygons and Circles.pdf
compact_text: Refer to trapezoid CDFG with median HE. Let WX be the median of CDEH. Find WX.
annotat_text: Refer to trapezoid $CDFG$ with median $\overline{HE}$. Let $\overline{WX}$ be the median of $CDEH$. Find $WX$.
